resources.string: "Global search allows you to find everything you need on your device. Use shortcuts in the Notification shade and App vault, or just swipe on your Home screen to open search. Search among all items saved on your device: apps, settings, contacts, messages, notes, emails, files, and more. With third-party search engine support, you can also search for news, videos, books, apps, and music online. If you have any questions, feel free to drop us a line: misearch-feedback@xiaomi.com"
